summary: i feel like there are three versions of taylor. theres the country taylor, who are all innocent, cute, and ~banjo~. “america’s...
body:
i feel like there are three versions of taylor. theres the country taylor, who are all innocent, cute, and ~banjo~. “america’s sweetheart.” then out of no where she emerges as 1989 taylor, the popular girl with the best clothes and most friends, but a girl who was getting stuff thrown at her and she was wearing down. then, when she fell apart, she grew into a strong, confident, powerful woman.

like it’s weird, i just cannot imagine reputation taylor as 1989 taylor, and as country taylor. they even look like 3 different people! and then the old song she performs just remind me that it’s all one amazing person who has done so many amazing songs. i can’t wait to see who she becomes next.
